Author: blackjok3r#3181
Content: It seems that with all nodes clustered in EU we are having a huge problem with fairness, I'm earning nothing lol, but my node is free using extra VM on my main notary. I had some ideas about this, but we need the log stuff setup, need to wait until some ppl have free time and get cfek network up maybe to test some iguana changes. We are lucky with labs being a 2 month fork, if we can make an iguana that is less dependent on pings we can switch to it quite fast.
